                    <h4>The Team Champion of October is Mothercare Kazan MEGA.</h4>
                    <p>
                        On November 22th, a group of thieves visited Mothercare MEGA Kazan store. Thanks to the quick
                        reaction of the store staff, the theft of 8 Gusti jackets at a retail price of 7999 rubles was
                        prevented. Colleagues are actively working in the trading floor to maximize sales and minimize
                        losses on a daily basis, for what we thank them on behalf of the Company.
                        <br>
